title: LivePix20Delux.rar
description:
Live Pix Delux
LivePix 2.0 Deluxe is award-winning, photo-editing software that lets you produce beautiful photo-quality projects from your home PC. Special effects tools - red-eye removal, cloning, retouching, automatic color correction, and distortion - enhance photos, and Intelligent Templates allow you to turn your everyday photos into fun photo projects. LivePix 2.0 Deluxe also includes a fully-integrated, multimedia e-mail application and has direct links with major online photo networks so photos and projects can be shared easily and quickly with family and friends.
